    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Estimate your conception date, fertile window, and pregnancy timeline from your due date or last period.</p>

    <%# Ad: leaderboard — placed below content heading per AdSense best practices %>
